achievement.name: Edubadge account complete

criteria.narrative:
To qualify for this edubadge:

*  you successfully created an eduID,
* you successfully linked your institution to your eduID,
*  you can store and manage them safely in your backpack.

achievement.description:
### Welcome to edubadges. Let your life long learning begin! ###

You are now ready to collect all your edubadges in your backpack. In your backpack you can store and manage them safely.

Share them anytime you like and with whom you like.

Edubadges are visual representations of your knowledge, skills and competences.

criteria.narrative: Team members are nominated for this badge by their peers and recognized upon review by Example Corp management.

achievement.description: This badge recognizes the development of the capacity to collaborate within a group environment.
achievement.name: Teamwork
